description: BAtlas tentatively (hollow symbol and question mark) places this road station, mentioned in the Peutinger map on a route between Augusta Vindelicum and Abodiacum, in the vicinity of modern Landsberg am Lech in Bavaria (see also Rathmann).
details: The Barrington Atlas Directory notes: on road between Augusta Vindelicum and Abodiacum GER
